Title: Address Allows for Invalid Phone Numbers

Description: The home and mobile phone number fields in Address accepts any numerical value below 32 digits.

The minimal steps necessary to reproduce: Register or login to an account, click on user's name and open my addresses, 
click on update and enter a numerical value greater than 10 digits into either the home or mobile number fields.

Environment: Microsoft Edge

Expected results: Rejection of the update and error message stating the need for a valid number for the field.

Assigned to: Andre Baptiste

Severity: Minor